sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant API as FastAPI Documents API
    participant ProjectService as Project Service
    participant Storage as Local Storage
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Queue as RQ / Redis
    participant Worker as Ingestion Worker

    User->>API: POST /api/projects/{project_id}/documents
    API->>ProjectService: verify project exists
    ProjectService->>DB: SELECT project by project_id
    DB-->>ProjectService: project found
    API->>API: validate file type and size
    API->>Storage: write file to data/uploads/{project_id}/{document_id}/
    Storage-->>API: storage_path
    API->>DB: INSERT document(status=uploaded)
    API->>DB: INSERT ingestion_job(status=queued)
    API->>Queue: enqueue(job_id, project_id, document_id)
    Queue-->>API: queued
    API-->>User: document + ingestion_job
    Queue->>Worker: deliver ingestion job
    Worker->>DB: later updates job/document status
